Interface GTNetHistoryquoteJpaRepository

All Superinterfaces:
org.springframework.data.repository.CrudRepository<GTNetHistoryquote,Integer>, org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<GTNetHistoryquote,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListCrudRepository<GTNetHistoryquote,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.ListPagingAndSortingRepository<GTNetHistoryquote,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.PagingAndSortingRepository<GTNetHistoryquote,Integer>, org.springframework.data.repository.query.QueryByExampleExecutor<GTNetHistoryquote>, org.springframework.data.repository.Repository<GTNetHistoryquote,Integer>
public interface GTNetHistoryquoteJpaRepository extends org.springframework.data.jpa.repository.JpaRepository<GTNetHistoryquote,Integer>
Repository for GTNetHistoryquote entities. Provides access to historical (EOD) price data for FOREIGN instruments in the GTNet pool. This table is only used for instruments that do NOT exist in the local database (where GTNetInstrument.isLocalInstrument() returns false). For local instruments, historical data is stored in the standard Historyquote table instead.
